description:
OneAutomata Log Client is the latest Logging library that supports centralized logging. Write and control logs that include attachments, performance logs, exceptions, trace logs, monitoring logs, information logs, development logs, request logs and so much more, all to a centralized location for viewing, filtering, notifying. Works with OneAutomata Web Application, and OneAutomata Cloud logging.

Use OneAutomata Cloud or dowload OneAutomata Web to store and view logs for FREE. Host Logging in a centralized location, gather log files, data, and event logs from different applications and servers.
releaseNotes:
Download the latest release of OneAutomata Web to work with this .NET library.
Database upgrade scripts available for older versions: http://www.oneautomata.com/Help/
